 Best WordPress Restaurant Themes Compared (2019)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-restaurant-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-restaurant-themes/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 05 Apr 2019 10:35:25 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"best restaurant themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"restaurant themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"restaurant wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=230338\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:665:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress themes for your restaurant website? A restaurant website usually includes a menu, images, and other important features to entice hungry customers. However, creating a professional website for your restaurant all starts with selecting an attractive, functional theme. In this article, we&#8217;ll share the 20 best WordPress restaurant themes [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-restaurant-themes/\">20 Best WordPress Restaurant Themes Compared (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24469:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress themes for your restaurant website? A restaurant website usually includes a menu, images, and other important features to entice hungry customers. However, creating a professional website for your restaurant all starts with selecting an attractive, functional theme.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the 20 best WordPress restaurant themes currently on the market.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-foodica/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Foodica\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Foodica</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-foodica/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Foodica\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/foodica.jpg\" alt=\"Foodica\" width=\"775\" height=\"339\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230354\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/foodica.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/foodica-300x131.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/foodica-768x336.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Foodica is a WordPress theme for restaurants, recipe websites, food bloggers, and magazines. It has multiple color schemes, a recipe index to post tempting recipes, and ad space to earn money from your website. Foodica supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a>, and it has an image slider to display mouthwatering food photos.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-belise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Belise\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Belise</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-belise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Belise\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/belise.jpg\" alt=\"Belise\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230355\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/belise.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/belise-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/belise-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Belise is a multipurpose WordPress restaurant theme. It comes with a 1-click demo installer to launch your restaurant website. Belise is <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/seo-friendly/\" title=\"How to Make Your WordPress Site SEO Friendly\">optimized for SEO</a> and speed. It comes with custom backgrounds, mega menus, and a powerful live customizer. It has WooCommerce integration to sell food online. The theme is translation-ready so you can <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)\">create a multilingual website</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hestia Coffee\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Hestia Coffee</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hestia Coffee\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/hestiacoffee.jpg\" alt=\"Hestia coffee\" width=\"775\" height=\"339\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230356\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/hestiacoffee.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/hestiacoffee-300x131.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/hestiacoffee-768x336.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hestia Coffee is a template used by the Hestia Pro theme for WordPress. It&#8217;s a perfect theme for your restaurant website. With all the features of Hestia Pro, you can create a multipurpose site or coffee blog easily. It has parallax scrolling, elegant homepage sections, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 BEST WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared\">eCommerce</a> support, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-downtown/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Downtown\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Downtown</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-downtown/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Downtown\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/downtown.jpg\" alt=\"Downtown\" width=\"1239\" height=\"575\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230357\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/downtown.jpg 1239w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/downtown-300x139.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/downtown-768x356.jpg 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/downtown-1024x475.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1239px) 100vw, 1239px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Downtown is a WordPress restaurant theme built specifically to create beautiful restaurant websites, food blogs, and online recipe magazines. It&#8217;s a smart choice for chefs to share their recipes in a professional, modern style. It has a custom logo, social share icons, widgets, and Google Maps to display your location. Downtown has a stunning <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\" title=\"11 Best WordPress Slider Plugins (Compared)\">homepage slider</a> to display your food photos.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/restaurant-and-cafe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Restaurant and Cafe\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Restaurant and Cafe</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/restaurant-and-cafe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Restaurant and Cafe\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurantcafe.jpg\" alt=\"Restaurant and Cafe\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230359\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurantcafe.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurantcafe-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurantcafe-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re just starting your restaurant business and looking for an affordable WordPress theme, then go for Restaurant and Cafe. It&#8217;s a free WordPress restaurant theme with basic features to create a beautiful food or bakery website. It comes with a restaurant menu section, testimonials section, an online reservation system, and an image slider. You can use this theme to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">create an online food store</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-ambiance/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ambiance\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Ambiance Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-ambiance/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ambiance\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ambiancepro.jpg\" alt=\"Ambiance Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230360\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ambiancepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ambiancepro-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/ambiancepro-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Ambiance Pro is a modern WordPress theme for restaurant websites. It&#8217;s built on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-genesis/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Genesis Framework\" rel=\"nofollow\">Genesis theme framework</a> which makes it a powerful theme. It allows you to display images and featured posts on the homepage. Ambiance Pro has a customizable header, widgets, theme options, and page templates.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-delicio/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Delicio\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Delicio</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-delicio/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Delicio\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/delicio.jpg\" alt=\"Delicio\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230361\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/delicio.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/delicio-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/delicio-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Delicio is a stylish WordPress theme to create a restaurant, coffee shop, or bakery website. It has a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared\">drag and drop page builder</a>, sliding sidebar, welcome message area, food menu, Google Maps support, and a responsive design. Delicio has <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce support</a> to sell online. It has a team section to display photos of your restaurant&#8217;s staff and chefs.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-carbone/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Carbone\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Carbone</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-carbone/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Carbone\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/carbone.jpg\" alt=\"Carbone\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230362\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/carbone.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/carbone-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/carbone-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Carbone is an elegant WordPress restaurant and cafe theme. It features a menu management system, online reservation form, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared\">page builders</a> support, and a live theme customizer. Carbone is fully <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">optimized for SEO</a> and speed performance. It&#8217;s translation-ready and can be used to create a multilingual restaurant blog or website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/restaurante/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Restaurante\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Restaurante</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/restaurante/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Restaurante\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurante.jpg\" alt=\"Restaurante\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230363\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurante.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurante-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/restaurante-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Restaurante is a free WordPress theme for your restaurant, barbecue, grill house, fast food, pizzerias, or other food-related website. It has a customizable background, header, and menu. Restaurante supports open graph and Twitter cards to gain popularity on social media channels. It has both multi-column and full-width templates.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-cafe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Cafe Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Cafe Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-cafe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Cafe Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cafepro.jpg\" alt=\"Cafe Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230364\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cafepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cafepro-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/cafepro-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Cafe Pro is a WordPress <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-genesis/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Genesis Framework\" rel=\"nofollow\">Genesis</a> theme. It can be used to create a beautiful and modern cafe website. The theme is perfect for a full-fledged restaurant or food blog. It has a parallax design, homepage widgets, menu system, online reservation, location support, and more. Cafe Pro comes with custom page templates and theme options to design your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert\">landing pages</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-igloo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Igloo\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Igloo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-igloo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Igloo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/igloo.jpg\" alt=\"Igloo\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230365\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/igloo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/igloo-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/igloo-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Igloo is a unique and powerful WordPress restaurant theme. It allows you to post your food photos professionally via a built-in <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"8 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared\">image gallery</a>. It has an amazing menu management system to display starters, main courses, and desserts with their prices. Igloo has multiple color schemes and 4 content types. It has custom widgets and is optimized for speed.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-seasons/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Seasons\" rel=\"nofollow\">12. Seasons</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-seasons/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Seasons\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/seasons.jpg\" alt=\"Seasons\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230366\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/seasons.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/seasons-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/seasons-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Seasons is a professional restaurant WordPress theme. It includes multiple layouts for a cafe, bar, restaurant, or other food-based websites. Like other restaurant themes, it has a food menu system and allows online reservations. It comes with a unique slideshow that can be used to display events, food photos, menus, and more. Seasons supports a blog template for food bloggers.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-listee/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Listee\" rel=\"nofollow\">13. Listee</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-listee/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Listee\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/listee.jpg\" alt=\"Listee\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230367\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/listee.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/listee-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/listee-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Listee is a business directory and listing theme for WordPress. If you want to create a list of local restaurants, then Listee is the perfect choice. It has a responsive layout, flexible search system, front-end list submissions, and a live theme customizer. It comes with a drag and drop page builder to create landing pages and business directories.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-petit/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Petit\" rel=\"nofollow\">14. Petit</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-petit/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Petit\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/petit.jpg\" alt=\"Petit\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230368\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/petit.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/petit-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/petit-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Petit is a food recipe theme for WordPress websites. On the homepage, there&#8217;s a featured area and carousel slider to post your recipes. It has a rating system to allow your users to rate the recipes and request more cuisines. Petit features custom widgets, recipe shortcodes, a theme options panel, and an Instagram widget. With the custom posts feature, you can easily separate a recipe post and display it on the homepage.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-mise-en-place/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mise En Place\" rel=\"nofollow\">15. Mise En Place</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-mise-en-place/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mise En Place\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/miseenplace.jpg\" alt=\"Mise En Place\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230369\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/miseenplace.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/miseenplace-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/miseenplace-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Mise En Place is a WordPress theme for chefs and restaurants. It supports custom logos, Google Fonts, unlimited colors, and a live customizer to style your website. It has a page builder to drag and drop features and content. The menu can be added with thumbnails and you can display it in the sidebar using a widget. Mise En Place has <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce integration</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/lzrestaurant/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lzrestaurant\" rel=\"nofollow\">16. Lzrestaurant</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/lzrestaurant/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lzrestaurant\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/lzrestaurant.jpg\" alt=\"Lzrestaurant\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230370\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/lzrestaurant.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/lzrestaurant-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/lzrestaurant-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Lzrestaurant is another free WordPress restaurant theme. It&#8217;s built for food critics and bloggers to write about cafes, restaurants, bars, and food businesses. It can also be used to sell food reviews. The testimonials section allows you to collect feedback from users on the critics. Lzrestaurant has social media integration, an SEO-friendly design, and a lightweight layout.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/quna/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Quna\" rel=\"nofollow\">17. Quna</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/quna/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Quna\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/quna.jpg\" alt=\"Quna\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230371\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/quna.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/quna-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/quna-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Quna is a minimal WordPress theme for restaurant and cafe websites. It has a post archive page to save your food blogs and recipes for users. It comes with social media support, and you can display food photos from your Instagram feed. It allows you to import the demo data and change the content to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-food-recipe-website/\" title=\"How to Create a Food &#038; Recipe Website (and Make Money)\">launch your restaurant website and make money</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-umami/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Umami\" rel=\"nofollow\">18. Umami</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-umami/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Umami\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/umami.jpg\" alt=\"Umami\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230351\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/umami.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/umami-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/umami-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Umami is a modern restaurant theme for WordPress. It has WooCommerce support to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">create an online store</a> and sell your food products. It comes with a fullscreen background slideshow to display food photos. The navigation menu is in the sidebar with your restaurant&#8217;s hours of operation, address, and social icons. Umami has a powerful system to display your restaurant&#8217;s menu in your pages, widget areas, and posts.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-moonrise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Moonrise\" rel=\"nofollow\">19. Moonrise</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-moonrise/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Moonrise\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/moonrise.jpg\" alt=\"Moonrise\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230352\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/moonrise.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/moonrise-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/moonrise-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Moonrise is a WordPress theme for restaurants, cafes, bars, and taverns. It has multiple templates including a 1-page template, blog template, inner-pages templates, and more. Moonrise has a long homepage with up to 7 sections to display your food menu, services, slideshow, contact details, widgets, and content. It offers easy customization to add your logo, change fonts, create image galleries, and manage theme colors.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-salt-pepper/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Salt and Pepper\" rel=\"nofollow\">20. Salt and Pepper</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-salt-pepper/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Salt and Pepper\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/saltpepper.jpg\" alt=\"Salt and Pepper\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230353\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/saltpepper.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/saltpepper-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/saltpepper-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Salt and Pepper is a WordPress recipe theme used to share tempting recipes and cooking tips with your users. It has all the standard website pages including about, contact, blog, and more. The theme comes with a drag and drop layout to easily add features and content on your website. It has <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPML\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a> support to create a translation-ready site or blog.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress restaurant themes. You may also want to check out our list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-themes/\" title=\"21 Best WordPress Real Estate Themes (Compared)\">best WordPress real estate themes</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-restaurant-themes/\">20 Best WordPress Restaurant Themes Compared (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-restaurant-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"How to Make an Online Portfolio on WordPress (Step by Step)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://www.isitwp.com/make-an-online-portfolio/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/make-an-online-portfolio/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 04 Apr 2019 10:19:23 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"how to make an online portfolio\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"make an online portfolio\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"make an online portfolio with wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"online portfolio\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"online portfolio with wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=229729\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:610:\"<p>Do you want to make an online portfolio to impress your potential clients? An ideal portfolio presents your work in a beautiful, professional way. Using WordPress, you can put your portfolio online on your website to get more business and boost your revenue. In this article, we&#8217;ll show you how to easily make an online [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/make-an-online-portfolio/\">How to Make an Online Portfolio on WordPress (Step by Step)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12319:\"<p>Do you want to make an online portfolio to impress your potential clients? An ideal portfolio presents your work in a beautiful, professional way. Using WordPress, you can put your portfolio online on your website to get more business and boost your revenue.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you how to easily make an online portfolio with WordPress.</p>\n<h3>Why Should You Make an Online Portfolio?</h3>\n<p>An online portfolio brings many opportunities on board. When presented well, your work&#8217;s quality will truly shine which will impress your site&#8217;s visitors, and they&#8217;ll become your ambassadors.</p>\n<p>There&#8217;re many reasons to create an online portfolio. We&#8217;re listing a few below so you&#8217;ll understand the primary benefits of having your own portfolio page:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>If you have a business website, you most likely share the services you offer. You should also display your portfolio to show your potential clients your previous accomplishments. A portfolio is visual proof you can perform the services you&#8217;re offering.</li>\n<li>When someone asks you about your portfolio, you won&#8217;t need to send it to them by mail or fax. You can simply share the link to your portfolio page.</li>\n<li>An online portfolio page improves your website&#8217;s search engine rankings.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Your online portfolio will not only help get you more business, it also connects you with like-minded people who&#8217;re looking to expand their businesses in the same direction. However, you&#8217;ll need to make sure your portfolio looks professional and interesting to reap these benefits.</p>\n<h3>What Does a Good Online Portfolio Look Like?</h3>\n<p>Portfolios can be different for each business or niche. For example, a website development agency would likely display the websites they&#8217;d made; whereas a real estate business would show their construction projects.</p>\n<p>The use of visual content in an engaging way can have more impact than plain, flat text. You can build an eye-catching portfolio by showing your best work first.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfolioexample.jpg\" alt=\"Portfolio example\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229820\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfolioexample.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfolioexample-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfolioexample-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>With a WordPress website, you can use an image gallery or photo slider to present your portfolio. If you use an image gallery plugin, you can also add text accompanying the images to explain your work. The more presentable a portfolio you make, the more you&#8217;ll engage with your users.</p>\n<p>That said, let&#8217;s take a look at how you can build a beautiful online portfolio with WordPress.</p>\n<h3>Building an Online Portfolio with WordPress</h3>\n<p>Now that you know why do you need an online portfolio, and what makes your portfolio look good, it&#8217;s time we walk you through each step of creating an online portfolio from scratch.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> If you already have a website, then you can directly go to the 3rd step.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 1: Choosing a Domain Name and Web Hosting</strong></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re just starting out, the first thing you&#8217;ll need is a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\" title=\"What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)\">domain name and web hosting</a>. You can buy a domain from any of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/choose-best-domain-name-registrar/\" title=\"How to Choose the Best Domain Name Registrar\">top domain name registrars</a> on the market. A simple domain name typically costs $11 / year.</p>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll find many <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/\" title=\"Top 10 Web Hosting Companies (Real Reviews, No B.S)\">web hosting</a> companies with different offers.</p>\n<p>We recommend using <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a>. It&#8217;s the most popular web hosting provider and an officially recommended WordPress hosting partner.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1.png\" alt=\"bluehost-register-domain-name-free\" width=\"740\" height=\"404\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228494\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1-300x164.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>For our users, they&#8217;re offering a free domain name and a massive discount on web hosting. It&#8217;ll save you a ton of money right off the bat when creating your online portfolio.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 2: Installing WordPress</strong></p>\n<p>WordPress is the world&#8217;s most <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-website-builders-for-beginners-compared/\" title=\"10 Best Website Builders for Beginners Compared\">popular website builder</a> thanks to its great flexibility and features. It enables you to build an online portfolio exactly how you want to.</p>\n<p>After purchasing a domain name and web hosting, you&#8217;ll need to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-complete-wordpress-installation-tutorial/\" title=\"How to Install WordPress – The Complete WordPress Installation Tutorial\">install WordPress</a>. If you&#8217;re using <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a>, then you can use their 1-click installer to install WordPress on your hosting account.</p>\n<p>Once installed, you can go ahead and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website - Step by Step (with Pictures)\">make a website with WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>Next, you can take a look at the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-themes/\">best WordPress themes</a> and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-plugins/\">plugins</a> to craft and customize your site. It&#8217;s very simple and doesn&#8217;t require any coding knowledge.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 3: Using WordPress Portfolio Themes</strong></p>\n<p>WordPress has a large collection of free and premium portfolio themes. You can find free themes on WordPress.org website. Simply search for the &#8216;portfolio&#8217; term and it&#8217;ll display all the themes that can be used to make an online portfolio.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/searchportfoliothemes.jpg\" alt=\"Search for portfolio themes\" width=\"775\" height=\"435\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229818\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/searchportfoliothemes.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/searchportfoliothemes-300x168.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/searchportfoliothemes-768x431.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also find hundreds of other themes/templates on the internet.</p>\n<p>For this guide, we&#8217;ll be using MyThemeShop&#8217;s <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mythemeshop-portfolio/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Portfolio\" rel=\"nofollow\">Portfolio</a> theme. For more details, you should check out this article on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-install-a-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"How to install a WordPress theme\">how to install a WordPress theme</a>.</p>\n<p>Once installed, you can select a layout. It offers 2 designs: blog portfolio and default portfolio. The default portfolio template shows your images on the home screen with big thumbnails.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfoliotheme.jpg\" alt=\"Portfolio theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229821\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfoliotheme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfoliotheme-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfoliotheme-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can add the portfolio items from your WordPress admin backend. The theme allows you to add filters in the portfolio and organize your work to make browsing easy for your visitors. You can also select the number of columns to display the images.</p>\n<p>There&#8217;re many other useful features in the theme like resizing images, portfolio navigation, sidebar widgets, etc. You can make a powerful online portfolio to get attention from your potential clients.</p>\n<p>Not a fan of our example theme? No worries. You can use pretty much any WordPress portfolio theme to make your portfolio. The options and settings will be different for each theme, but you&#8217;ll still be able to get the desired result.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 4: Using WordPress Portfolio Plugins</strong></p>\n<p>While WordPress portfolio themes are solely focused on creating an online portfolio website, you can also use a multipurpose theme and then utilize plugins to add your portfolio into your web page. Simply check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/add-portfolio-wordpress-site-beginners-guide/\" title=\"How to Add a Portfolio to Your WordPress Site: Beginner’s Guide\">how to add a portfolio to your WordPress site</a>.</p>\n<p>You can search for free portfolio plugins in the WordPress.org plugins repository.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfolioplugins.jpg\" alt=\"Portfolio plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"375\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229822\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfolioplugins.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfolioplugins-300x145.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfolioplugins-768x372.jpg 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/portfolioplugins-330x160.jpg 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;d like to add premium features to your portfolio, then you can also find paid WordPress plugins on the internet. All of these plugins will have different features and options. You&#8217;ll need to do a little research and choose the perfect portfolio plugin to match your requirements.</p>\n<h3>What to Do After Making an Online Portfolio</h3>\n<p>When your online portfolio is ready, you shouldn&#8217;t stop there.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll need to promote it, so more people can see your work. There&#8217;re many ways to do that, including <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/\" title=\"9 Best Email Marketing Services Compared\">email marketing</a>, sharing on social media, and getting a word-of-mouth shoutout from the top influencers in your niche. You can also <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-start-a-blog-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Start a WordPress Blog (&#038; Make Extra Income)\">start a blog</a> and share your experience in an engaging, professional way.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll also need to optimize your portfolio website or pages for the search engines. It&#8217;ll help you get more organic traffic. SEO will lead the right people to your portfolio who were actively searching for a similar type of work. Check out our complete guide on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">best SEO tools to grow your website traffic</a>.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s all. We hope this guide helped you learn how to make an online portfolio with WordPress. You may also want to check out our article on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-set-up-google-optimize-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Use Google Optimize in WordPress (Step by Step)\">how to use Google Optimize in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/make-an-online-portfolio/\">How to Make an Online Portfolio on WordPress (Step by Step)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/make-an-online-portfolio/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"11 Best Intercom Alternatives for Better Communication\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"https://www.isitwp.com/intercom-alternatives/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/intercom-alternatives/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 03 Apr 2019 13:31:53 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"best intercom alternatives\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"intercom alternatives\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"intercom chat\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"intercom competitors\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"intercom livechat\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=229954\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:609:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Intercom alternatives and competitors? Intercom is a live chat software for sales and communication. It can be used for instant chatting with your website visitors to convert them into customers. Intercom can also be used as a marketing tool. However, it lacks several advanced features, so you may need [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/intercom-alternatives/\">11 Best Intercom Alternatives for Better Communication</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17101:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Intercom alternatives and competitors? Intercom is a live chat software for sales and communication. It can be used for instant chatting with your website visitors to convert them into customers. Intercom can also be used as a marketing tool. However, it lacks several advanced features, so you may need to check out other options that have fewer limitations.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best Intercom alternatives you can use to communicate with your customers.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"LiveChat\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. LiveChat</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/livechat-inc/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"LiveChat\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/livechatsoftware.png\" alt=\"LiveChat\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230336\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/livechatsoftware.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/livechatsoftware-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/livechatsoftware-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>LiveChat, Inc. is one of the most popular live chat and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-help-desk-plugins/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Help Desk Plugins for Customer Support\">help desk plugins for customer support</a>. It&#8217;s the oldest live chat software and works great on all operating systems. You can integrate LiveChat with WordPress and other <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-website-builders-for-beginners-compared/\" title=\"10 Best Website Builders for Beginners Compared\">major website builders</a> to improve the communication process with your customers.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s available in over 40 languages, which makes it a truly global software. The setup is easy and you can operate the chat from any device like your laptop, phone, tablet, etc. It has a clean interface to display on your website, and it serves as real competition to Intercom.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It costs $16 / month if billed annually. You can also sign up for a 30-day free trial.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/olark/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Olark\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Olark</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/olark/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Olark\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/olark.jpg\" alt=\"Olark\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229966\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/olark.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/olark-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/olark-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Olark is a live chat software for sales and customer support teams. It can be used to connect with your visitors, give support, and convert them into clients. It integrates with CRM, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 BEST WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared\">eCommerce solutions</a>, and other tools to transfer the data from the live chat software to your website.</p>\n<p>It comes with customization options to design the live chat box to match with the theme of your website. You can add beautiful colors and change the shape of the live chat box. As for features, Olark allows you to keep an eye on the chat volume, prioritization, and smart shifting of your staff to the most important chats. You can also get the chat reports in your inbox.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It costs $15 / month if billed annually. You can also sign up for a 2-week free trial to test the software.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/slack/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Slack\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Slack</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/slack/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Slack\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/slack-e1553153306174.png\" alt=\"Slack\" width=\"775\" height=\"244\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229967\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/slack-e1553153306174.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/slack-e1553153306174-300x94.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/slack-e1553153306174-768x242.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Slack is a web and app-based team collaboration software. It can be used for internal and external communication. You can use Slack to build channels and send messages to a larger user group. It also enables you to communicate privately with your team members and customers. It&#8217;s a different kind of software when compared to live chat software like Olark or LiveChat, Inc.</p>\n<p>With Slack, you can add multiple team members on a chat to respond to a customer. It can be integrated with many apps, tools, and services to easily share content during the chat.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It has a free plan with basic features. The premium version starts from $6.67 / month if billed annually.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/zopim/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Zendesk Chat\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Zendesk Chat</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/zopim/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Zendesk Chat\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/zendesk-1.png\" alt=\"Zendesk\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230426\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/zendesk-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/zendesk-1-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/zendesk-1-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Zendesk is another popular live chat software used to communicate with your customers from web, app, or messengers. It has a targeted and behavior-based chat option to connect with your visitors on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert\">landing pages</a>. You can instantly help those users to sign up for your service or complete a purchase.</p>\n<p>It comes with chat ratings, file sending, chatbots, online forms, and more. Zendesk Chat has a real-time dashboard to show active chats, incoming chats, chats in a queue, wait time, response time, and other activities from the software.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> The cost starts from $14 per agent / month. You can try their Enterprise level service during the free trial or sign up for the free Lite version (very limited features).</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/snapengage/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"SnapEngage\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. SnapEngage</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/snapengage/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"SnapEngage\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/snapengage.png\" alt=\"SnapEngage\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229957\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/snapengage.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/snapengage-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/snapengage-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>SnapEngage is an enterprise chat software for sales and support. It comes with a goal-driven chat platform for websites. SnapEngage integrates with Facebook Messenger, SMS-to-Chat, Tweet-to-Chat, WeChat, and other popular software to communicate with your users on any platform.</p>\n<p>Like other live chat software, it controls the flow of chats with bots and customized messages. You can customize the chat box design. It features analytics, safety and security of user information, and is HIPPA compliant for healthcare-related businesses. You can confidently use SnapEngage as an alternative to Intercom.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> The starting plan costs $16 per user / month if billed annually. All plans have a free trial to test the service.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/freshchat/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"FreshChat\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. FreshChat</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/freshchat/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"FreshChat\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/freshchat.png\" alt=\"FreshChat\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230019\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/freshchat.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/freshchat-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/freshchat-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>FreshChat is a messenger app and live chat service. It enables you to connect with your website visitors using bots and campaigns to convert them into customers. You can display a popup message to your users when they start to exit from your site. FreshChat allows you to send behavior-based messages to your users depending on which landing page they&#8217;re visiting.</p>\n<p>It comes with smart plugs, canned responses, private notes, desktop notifications, chat bots, and more. FreshChat can be integrated with Slack, Facebook Messenger, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shopify\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shopify</a>, WordPress, and other online applications.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It has a free version with limited monthly unique visitors. The paid plans start from $15 / month if billed annually.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/chaport/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Chaport\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Chaport</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/chaport/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Chaport\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/chaport.jpg\" alt=\"Chaport\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230062\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/chaport.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/chaport-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/chaport-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Chaport is a smart live chat plugin for WordPress websites. It includes registered operators, unlimited chat capacity, reporting, analytics, chat history, and email notifications. The free version of Chaport allows you to put 5 team members online at a time. You can upgrade to the premium plans for more features.</p>\n<p>Additionally, Chaport offers multilingual chat widgets, Zapier integration, and supports apps to use live chat from all your devices. It comes with visitor notes, auto-invitations, typing insights, and more.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It costs $9.80 / month if paid annually. The basic plan is free for up to 5 operators.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/comm100/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Comm100 Live Chat\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Comm100 Live Chat</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/comm100/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Comm100 Live Chat\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/commlivechat.png\" alt=\"Comm100 Live Chat\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230428\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/commlivechat.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/commlivechat-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/commlivechat-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Comm100 Live Chat is a perfect messaging and chat service for your website, apps, and social media properties. It works totally on user behavior and sends personalized messages to your users by analyzing their actions on your site.</p>\n<p>It comes with pre-chat surveys, eCommerce and CRM integrations, intelligent tracking, custom messages, and more. Comm100 Live Chat is a flexible platform to engage with your customers and website visitors. It offers pre-programmed messages to greet users and make them feel valued.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It costs $29 per agent / month.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.drift.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Drift\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Drift</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.drift.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Drift\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/drift-1.png\" alt=\"Drift\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230429\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/drift-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/drift-1-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/drift-1-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Drift is an excellent live chat software and marketing platform for small businesses. It helps you connect your sales team with potential customers. It has a Drift Bot that gives instant replies to your visitors to engage them in conversations. Drift enables you to work with the most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/\" title=\"9 Best Email Marketing Services Compared\">email marketing services</a> and other useful apps.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll get important features like a meetings scheduler, visitor intelligence, account-based marketing, automated help center, and more. Drift is easy to set up on your website and can be operated from mobile devices.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It costs $50 / month if billed annually. Drift also offers a free version with basic, very limited features.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pure-chat/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Pure Chat\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Pure Chat</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/pure-chat/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Pure Chat\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/purechat.png\" alt=\"Pure Chat\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230063\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/purechat.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/purechat-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/purechat-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Pure Chat is a free live chat service for high traffic websites. If you want a dedicated live chat operator, then Pure Chat is the best choice. It can connect with your website and displays a chat widget for users to connect with you.</p>\n<p>The free plan has unlimited chats, engagement hub, chat transcripts, custom widgets, supports up to 3 operators, apps for mobile devices, and more. It shows a pre-chat form to users, so they can fill in their personal information and you can connect with them once you&#8217;re online. Pure Chat can be a smart alternative to Intercom.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It costs $39 / month if billed annually for the premium version with the most options.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smartsupp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Smartsupp\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Smartsupp</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smartsupp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Smartsupp\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/smartsupp.png\" alt=\"Smartsupp\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230064\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/smartsupp.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/smartsupp-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/smartsupp-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Smartsupps is an affordable live chat service to integrate with your website and apps like WordPress, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a>, Magento, etc. It integrates with Google Analytics to share reports from your chats and you can also create custom reports for the live chat sessions.</p>\n<p>With Smartsupps, you can enjoy the free live chat service. Though, it only saves the chat history for 14 days. The free plan has basic customization options for the chat box.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It comes with a free plan. The premium plan costs $8 per agent / per month.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the best Intercom alternatives. You may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/mailchimp-alternatives/\" title=\"MailChimp Competitors – 7 Popular Alternatives to MailChimp\">popular MailChimp alternatives and competitors</a> to automate your email marketing.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/intercom-alternatives/\">11 Best Intercom Alternatives for Better Communication</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://www.isitwp.com/intercom-alternatives/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"How to Create Email Accounts for Your Domain Name\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-email-accounts-for-your-domain-name/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-email-accounts-for-your-domain-name/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 01 Apr 2019 18:48:42 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"create email accounts\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"create email accounts with G suite\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"email accounts for domain name\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"email accounts for your domain\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=229826\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:627:\"<p>Do you want to create branded email accounts from your domain name? After purchasing your domain name, you&#8217;ll have the opportunity to get associated email accounts with it. Using an email address branded with your domain name is a great way to give off professional vibe to your potential customers. You can even create multiple [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-email-accounts-for-your-domain-name/\">How to Create Email Accounts for Your Domain Name</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22331:\"<p>Do you want to create branded email accounts from your domain name? After purchasing your domain name, you&#8217;ll have the opportunity to get associated email accounts with it. Using an email address branded with your domain name is a great way to give off professional vibe to your potential customers. You can even create multiple email accounts associated with your domain, so your team members can better represent your brand. </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you how to properly create email accounts for your domain name and use them to send emails.</p>\n<h3>Why Should You Create Email Accounts for Your Domain Name?</h3>\n<p>Most email addresses you&#8217;ll see end with gmail.com, live.com, aol.com, etc. These email addresses are great for personal use, but aren&#8217;t recommended for businesses, or anyone else looking to portray a professional image.</p>\n<p>First of all, if your name is relatively common, then you most likely won&#8217;t get your desired email address. You&#8217;ll end up adding numbers or additional letters to your email address (ex: dan.brown321@gmail.com) which doesn&#8217;t look professional. In fact, it looks downright spammy.</p>\n<p>If you have a business then you&#8217;ll need a simple email address that represents yourself and your company name.</p>\n<p>You can achieve that by creating email addresses for your domain name. Check out this example:</p>\n<p><strong>Your Domain Name:</strong></p>\n<p>www.example.com</p>\n<p><strong>Your Email Address:</strong></p>\n<p>dan.brown@example.com or dan@example.com</p>\n<p>From the above example, you can easily see the difference between a personal and a professional email address. Emails sent using your own domain name will quickly gain the trust of your users, and it&#8217;s a great way to conduct business-related communication.</p>\n<h3>Setting Up Email Accounts for Your Domain Name</h3>\n<p>To create business email accounts, you&#8217;ll need a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\" title=\"What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)\">domain name and web hosting</a>. </p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> If you already have a domain name and web hosting, then skip to the next step.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 1. Register a Domain Name and Web Hosting</strong></p>\n<p>You can check out the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/choose-best-domain-name-registrar/\" title=\"How to Choose the Best Domain Name Registrar\">top domain name registrars</a> to purchase your professional business name online. Not only can you buy a domain name, but these registrars will also suggest other business name options.</p>\n<p>After getting your domain name, you&#8217;ll need to connect it with a web hosting account. You&#8217;ll need to do this before you can create email accounts for your domain name.</p>\n<p>We recommend using <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> for web hosting. It&#8217;s the most popular hosting company in the world.</p>\n<p>For IsItWP users, they&#8217;re offering a free domain name, a free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on web hosting.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1.png\" alt=\"bluehost-register-domain-name-free\" width=\"740\" height=\"404\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228494\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-refer-1-300x164.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Once you have your domain name and web hosting, you&#8217;ll need to log into your Bluehost account to create your email accounts.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 2. Log Into Your Hosting cPanel and Create Your Email Accounts</strong></p>\n<p>First, you&#8217;ll need to log into your cPanel account. If you&#8217;re using Bluehost, then the cPanel will look like this:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bluehost-cpanel.jpg\" alt=\"Bluehost cPanel\" width=\"774\" height=\"346\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230792\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bluehost-cpanel.jpg 774w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bluehost-cpanel-300x134.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bluehost-cpanel-768x343.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 774px) 100vw, 774px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll need to click the &#8216;Email and Office&#8217; tab from the left-hand navigation menu and click on the &#8216;Manage&#8217; button to get started.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/manage-emails.jpg\" alt=\"Manage emails\" width=\"775\" height=\"334\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230793\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/manage-emails.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/manage-emails-300x129.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/manage-emails-768x331.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>On the next page, you&#8217;ll find multiple tabs. Under the &#8216;Add Email Account&#8217; tab, you can enter your desired account name. Try something like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>dan@example.com</li>\n<li>info@example.com</li>\n<li>hello@example.com</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In the above example, &#8216;dan,&#8217; &#8216;info,&#8217; and &#8216;hello&#8217; are the usernames and &#8216;example.com&#8217; is your business/domain name.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/create-email-accounts.jpg\" alt=\"Create email accounts\" width=\"775\" height=\"395\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230794\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/create-email-accounts.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/create-email-accounts-300x153.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/create-email-accounts-768x391.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Make sure that you don&#8217;t enter your domain name in this field as it&#8217;s already there. You don&#8217;t want to end up as &#8216;dan@example.com@example.com!&#8217;</p>\n<p>After choosing your account name, you can enter a secure password. If you can&#8217;t think of a secure enough password, Bluehost will offer to generate a random password for you which you can save before continuing.</p>\n<p>Next, you can add the Mailbox Quota. This quota depends on your hosting plan and we recommend you leave it as-is. By default, it&#8217;s set to 500 MB, which is a decent amount of space for an email account. You should have more than enough space; however, you can always increase or decrease it later, if needed.</p>\n<p>Click on the &#8216;Create Account&#8217; button to complete the process. You can make multiple email accounts for your domain name by repeating the above steps.</p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;re done, simply go to the &#8216;Email Accounts&#8217; tab to view all of the email addresses you created.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/email-accounts.jpg\" alt=\"Email accounts\" width=\"775\" height=\"306\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230795\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/email-accounts.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/email-accounts-300x118.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/email-accounts-768x303.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Step 3. Access Your Email Account</strong></p>\n<p>To access your email accounts, you can click on the &#8216;Access Webmail&#8217; link next to an email address. It&#8217;ll open up an email client where you can see your new emails. You can also send emails from there.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/access-webmail.jpg\" alt=\"Access webmail\" width=\"775\" height=\"380\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230796\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/access-webmail.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/access-webmail-300x147.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/access-webmail-768x377.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>If you want to set up your email account on other devices, like your mobile phone, then click on the &#8216;Connect Devices&#8217; link; and then click on the &#8216;Set Up Mail Client&#8217; option.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;ll display the information you need to configure your email account on all major applications/devices. Luckily, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> offers automatic configurations to many apps and devices.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/setup-mail-clients.jpg\" alt=\"Set up email clients\" width=\"775\" height=\"450\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230797\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/setup-mail-clients.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/setup-mail-clients-300x174.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/setup-mail-clients-768x446.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can also find manual configuration options on that page for devices and applications that aren&#8217;t listed in the auto-config section.</p>\n<h3>Setting Up an Email Account with G Suite</h3>\n<p>Now that you have your email accounts, you can connect them with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gsuite/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"G Suite\" rel=\"nofollow\">G Suite by Google Cloud</a> and use them from there. It&#8217;ll make your emailing experience a lot easier than using webmail by <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Why You Should Connect Your Email Account with G Suite</strong></p>\n<p>The email clients offered by Bluehost, or any other web hosting company, are not as simple or tidy as Gmail. Also, you won&#8217;t get additional apps like you will with G Suite. Webmail is a simple application to send and receive emails with no other features.</p>\n<p>However, you may use G Suite daily on your laptop and phone. G Suite includes all the popular Google apps like Gmail, Google Photos, Docs, Drive, etc.</p>\n<p>Once you connect your business email accounts with G Suite, you can access all their apps and features.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a premium service which means you&#8217;ll need to pay an additional cost other than the cost of a domain name and web hosting, but it&#8217;s well worth the price. <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gsuite/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"G Suite\" rel=\"nofollow\">G Suite</a> plans start from $5 per user / month. It&#8217;ll include resources separately for the number of accounts you purchase.</p>\n<p>First, you&#8217;ll need to go the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gsuite/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"G Suite\" rel=\"nofollow\">G Suite</a> website and select a plan to get started.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/selectplan.jpg\" alt=\"Select a plan\" width=\"775\" height=\"368\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230828\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/selectplan.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/selectplan-300x142.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/selectplan-768x365.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>On the next page, you&#8217;ll need to enter basic details about your business to continue.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/get-started-gsuite.jpg\" alt=\"Get started with G Suite\" width=\"775\" height=\"420\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230829\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/get-started-gsuite.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/get-started-gsuite-300x163.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/get-started-gsuite-768x416.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>After that, you&#8217;ll be asked if you have a domain name. Since you purchased your domain name in the previous section, you can select the option &#8216;I have a domain&#8217; and click on the &#8216;Next&#8217; button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/havedomain.jpg\" alt=\"Have a domain\" width=\"775\" height=\"395\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230830\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/havedomain.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/havedomain-300x153.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/havedomain-768x391.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, enter your business name or domain name and click the &#8216;Next&#8217; button again.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterdomainname.jpg\" alt=\"Enter domain name\" width=\"775\" height=\"292\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230831\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterdomainname.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterdomainname-300x113.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterdomainname-768x289.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll need to add a username and password. This username will be the account name for your email and it&#8217;ll be attached to your domain name (dan@example.com).</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterusername.jpg\" alt=\"Enter username\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230832\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterusername.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterusername-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/enterusername-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Once signed up, you&#8217;ll see a success message showing that your account was created. This will be your primary email account (administrator account) for your domain name.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accountcreated.jpg\" alt=\"G Suite account created\" width=\"775\" height=\"186\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230833\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accountcreated.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accountcreated-300x72.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/accountcreated-768x184.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the &#8216;Go to Setup&#8217; button to complete the account setup.</p>\n<p>On the setup screen, you should add your team members or other users to create more accounts. Simply check the &#8216;I added all user email addresses currently using [this domain]&#8217; option and click on the &#8216;Next&#8217; button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/addedallusers.jpg\" alt=\"Add all users\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230834\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/addedallusers.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/addedallusers-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/addedallusers-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> If you have a single email account, then you can skip this step.</p>\n<p>Next, you&#8217;ll need to verify ownership for your domain name.</p>\n<p>Simply copy the meta tag, or upload an HTML file, to your hosting account for verification. Use only 1 method to verify domain ownership.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/metatag.jpg\" alt=\"Meta tag\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230835\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/metatag.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/metatag-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/metatag-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll need to log into your website and install the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/insert-headers-and-footers/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Insert Headers and Footers\" rel=\"nofollow\">Insert Headers and Footers</a> plugin to do this. For more details, you can read our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"How to Install a WordPress Plugin\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>Once the plugin&#8217;s activated, go to <strong>Settings &raquo; Insert Headers and Footer</strong> and enter the meta tag in the &#8216;Scripts in Header&#8217; text area.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/scriptsheader.jpg\" alt=\"Scripts in header\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230836\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/scriptsheader.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/scriptsheader-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/scriptsheader-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the &#8216;Save&#8217; button and go back to your G Suite page to check &#8216;I added the meta tag to my homepage&#8217; option.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyemail.jpg\" alt=\"Verify email account\" width=\"775\" height=\"286\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230837\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyemail.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyemail-300x111.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyemail-768x283.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll also need to enter MX records for your domain name to make the G Suite functional for your email accounts.</p>\n<p>The process of adding the MX records is quite similar for any domain name registrar. Since we&#8217;re using Bluehost, we&#8217;ll walk you through adding the entries in your Bluehost account.</p>\n<p>Log into your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bluehost\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> hosting account and visit the &#8216;Domains&#8217; page from the left-hand navigation menu.</p>\n<p>From there, you&#8217;ll need to select your domain name and click on the &#8216;Manage DNS records&#8217; link on the right side.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/managedns.jpg\" alt=\"Manage DNS\" width=\"775\" height=\"322\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230838\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/managedns.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/managedns-300x125.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/managedns-768x319.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Go back to G Suite&#8217;s website and check &#8216;I have opened the control panel for my domain&#8217; option. You&#8217;ll now see the MX record entries that you can copy from there.</p>\n<p>Now, you can come back to your Bluehost account and enter the MX records.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/entermxrecords.jpg\" alt=\"Enter MX records\" width=\"775\" height=\"260\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230839\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/entermxrecords.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/entermxrecords-300x101.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/entermxrecords-768x258.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Click on the &#8216;Add Record&#8217; button to continue.</p>\n<p>After that, go to G Suite&#8217;s website and check &#8216;I created the new MX records&#8217; option. You&#8217;ll also need to delete any existing MX record entries pointing to your domain name.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/createdmxrecords.jpg\" alt=\"Created MX records\" width=\"775\" height=\"192\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230840\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/createdmxrecords.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/createdmxrecords-300x74.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/createdmxrecords-768x190.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Once deleted, you&#8217;ll also need to save the MX records manually and check the &#8216;I saved the MX records&#8217; option.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyaccount.jpg\" alt=\"Verify domain name\" width=\"775\" height=\"363\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230841\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyaccount.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyaccount-300x141.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/verifyaccount-768x360.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Last, click on the &#8216;Verify Domain and Set Up Email&#8217; button to complete the process. For more specific details, you can follow our complete tutorial on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-a-professional-business-email-with-g-suite/\" title=\"How to Create a Professional Branded Business Email with G Suite\">how to create a business email with G Suite</a>.</p>\n<p>You can go ahead and log into your email account using Gmail or the G Suite website. As an administrator, you can also manage all additional email accounts for your domain name.</p>\n<p>We hope this guide helped you learn how to create email accounts for your domain name. You may also want to check out our article on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-a-free-business-email/\" title=\"How to Create a Free Business Email in Less than 5 Minutes\">how to create a free business email in less than 5 minutes</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-email-accounts-for-your-domain-name/\">How to Create Email Accounts for Your Domain Name</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-email-accounts-for-your-domain-name/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"10 Best Business Phone Services and Systems (2019)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-business-phone-services/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-business-phone-services/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 29 Mar 2019 08:26:25 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"best business phone services\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"grasshopper\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"nextiva\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"phonecom\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"ringcentral\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"small business phone service\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=228255\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:629:\"<p>Do you want the best business phone service for your WordPress site? Many small businesses integrate an online phone system on their websites to instantly connect with their users. It&#8217;s an additional service to live chat, email support, and other solutions on the market. In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best business phone services you [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-business-phone-services/\">10 Best Business Phone Services and Systems (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13969:\"<p>Do you want the best business phone service for your WordPress site? Many small businesses integrate an online phone system on their websites to instantly connect with their users. It&#8217;s an additional service to live chat, email support, and other solutions on the market.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best business phone services you can use on your WordPress website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextiva/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nextiva\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Nextiva</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextiva/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Nextiva\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nextiva.jpg\" alt=\"Nextiva\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228256\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nextiva.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nextiva-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/nextiva-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Nextiva is one of the most popular business phone and call forwarding services for small businesses. It&#8217;s easy to use and offers amazing features. Nextiva is an affordable service, which means <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-small-business-website-simple-steps/\" title=\"How to Create a Small Business Website in 5 Simple Steps (2019)\">small business websites</a> can easily benefit from it. It has a web-based panel to manage your calls, voicemails, and faxes.</p>\n<p>Nextiva has a VOIP service that enables you to do free domestic calling, call routing, transfer voicemails to emails, and more. Their VOIP service is advanced yet beginner-friendly and easy to use. Other than that, the primary perk of using Nextiva is that it&#8217;ll provide you with a registered toll-free number which means your users can connect with you for free. It also offers other services like <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-live-chat-software-compared/\" title=\"9 Best Live Chat Software Plugins Compared (2019)\">live chat</a>, call analytics, CRM, etc.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $19.95 / month with no setup fees.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/phone-com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Phone.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Phone.com</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/phone-com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Phone.com\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/phonecom.jpg\" alt=\"Phone.com\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228258\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/phonecom.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/phonecom-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/phonecom-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Phone.com is the best business phone service for small businesses. It comes with a call routing service, call forwarding, fax, caller ID, multi-line (conference) calling, and more. Phone.com has both app-based and web-based panels to manage calls online.</p>\n<p>They have a cheap business phone line for many European countries and Canada which lets their users expand their businesses to those countries. Phone.com offer integration with many CRM software on the market including Zoho and Salesforce.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It comes with pay-per-minute and unlimited pricing plans. Starting from $9.99 / month if paid annually.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ringcentral/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"RingCentral\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. RingCentral</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ringcentral/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"RingCentral\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ringcentral.jpg\" alt=\"RingCentral\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228259\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ringcentral.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ringcentral-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/ringcentral-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>RingCentral is a hassle-free business phone service that can be used by small-to-large scale businesses easily. Like all other top business phone services, RingCentral comes with a call waiting option, call transfers, a multi-line phone system, call forwarding, conference calls, video conferencing, and more.</p>\n<p>It enables you to share screens, make free calls with their toll-free option, and works great with third-party services like Microsoft, Gusto, Dropbox, etc. RingCentral has a simple portal to launch business phone services and manage calls from users.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $19.99 / month. RingCentral also offers other custom plans to fulfill your needs.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/8x8-phone-service/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"8x8\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. 8&#215;8</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/8x8-phone-service/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"8x8\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/8x8service.jpg\" alt=\"8x8 Business phone service\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228262\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/8x8service.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/8x8service-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/8x8service-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>8&#215;8 is a popular business phone service on the market. It&#8217;s a perfect fit for beginners who&#8217;re starting to add an internet business phone system on their websites. 8&#215;8 has fewer features than an average online phone solution, but it&#8217;s useful for small business owners.</p>\n<p>Their services include voicemail, automatic call answering, text, number sharing, and more. They offer several plans for their users to provide ease and reliability.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $24.99 / mo for each user (Also, 250 outbound minutes to the US and Canada)</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/grasshopper/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"GrassHopper\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. GrassHopper</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/grasshopper/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"GrassHopper\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/grasshopper.jpg\" alt=\"GrassHopper\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228264\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/grasshopper.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/grasshopper-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/grasshopper-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>GrassHopper is the best virtual phone system for small business owners. It comes with all the standard VOIP service features like call forwarding, voicemail, caller ID, etc. It enables you to make calls using a regular phone number. Their extensions can be used to make conference calls, which is great for inbound team meetings.</p>\n<p>The web and app-based portal is easy to use. It comes with toll-free numbers for the US, UK, and Canada. GrassHopper has multiple extensions for phone numbers, toll-free numbers, and vanity numbers to make calls online.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $29.99 / month (1 number and up to 3 extensions)</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.vonage.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Vonage\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Vonage</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.vonage.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Vonage\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/vonage.jpg\" alt=\"Vonage\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228268\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/vonage.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/vonage-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/vonage-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Vonage is another small business phone service that can be used for online calling. It comes with all the standard VOIP services, plus Amazon Chime, video calls, and more. Their premium services have more features and additional advanced technology for their users.</p>\n<p>Their web-based administration panel helps regulate calls, create users, and manage online communication in a smart way.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $19.99 / month.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.skype.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Skype\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Skype</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.skype.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Skype\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/skype.jpg\" alt=\"Skype\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228269\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/skype.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/skype-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/skype-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Skype is the most popular phone system to make voice calls and conduct video conferences in the world. It offers unlimited free calls to other Skype users via an internet connection. However, when you want to make calls to international or local numbers, then you&#8217;ll need their premium credits.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s powered by Microsoft, which means the service has a solid foundation. You can also get a local number which users can call to connect with you on Skype.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Basic version is free to download. Enterprise plan starting from $8.25 / month.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://voice.google.com/u/0/about\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Google Voice\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Google Voice</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://voice.google.com/u/0/about\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Google Voice\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/googlevoice.jpg\" alt=\"Google Voice\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228274\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/googlevoice.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/googlevoice-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/googlevoice-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Google Voice is a flexible business phone service. However, it has fewer options when compared to a fully virtual phone system. It&#8217;s handy for smart phone users and business owners using devices that support Google products.</p>\n<p>It has a free US-based number, voicemail service, call recording, and more. Google Voice helps create better communication between business owners and consumers.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> A free number to make calls, texts, and voicemails.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.voiceshot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Voiceshot\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Voiceshot</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.voiceshot.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Voiceshot\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/voiceshot.jpg\" alt=\"Voiceshot\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228271\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/voiceshot.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/voiceshot-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/voiceshot-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Voiceshot is an excellent business phone service for small websites. It comes with an auto respondent system to answer calls anytime which means you&#8217;re active even after business hours. Voiceshot allows you to send outbound messages to your users. You can also create custom, interactive outbound texts.</p>\n<p>It helps with call scheduling and sends alerts / reminders to you and your users about the call. Other features include emergency call alerts, integrations, and more.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Starting from $12 / month.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://callhippo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"CallHippo\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. CallHippo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://callhippo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"CallHippo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callhippo.jpg\" alt=\"CallHippo\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228273\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callhippo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callhippo-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/callhippo-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>CallHippo is one of the most popular virtual phone systems in the world. It has standard VOIP features like a phone number, caller ID, call forwarding, etc. You don&#8217;t need a desk phone to make calls using CallHippo as everything is managed from their online portal.</p>\n<p>It has a simple web-based portal to create users, manage calls, and more. You can also create departments and transfer calls to specific experts.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Basic set up is free for up to 2 users. Premium plans starting form $8 / month.</p>\n<p>We hope this guide helped you discover the best business phone services. If you liked this article, then you should also check out our guide on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-help-desk-plugins/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Help Desk Plugins for Customer Support\">9 best WordPress help desk plugins for customer support</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-business-phone-services/\">10 Best Business Phone Services and Systems (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-business-phone-services/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"dat