"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=229482\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:607:\"<p>Are you looking for popular alternatives to Wix? As one of the most popular website builders for beginners and startups, Wix is known for their easy-to-use drag and drop platform. Using Wix, you can create a basic website in mere minutes. However, if you want to expand your website, you&#8217;ll need to buy their expensive [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-wix-alternatives/\">9 Best Wix Alternatives to Easily Build a Site (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17238:\"<p>Are you looking for popular alternatives to Wix? As one of the most popular website builders for beginners and startups, Wix is known for their easy-to-use drag and drop platform. Using Wix, you can create a basic website in mere minutes. However, if you want to expand your website, you&#8217;ll need to buy their expensive premium extensions. As Wix becomes too costly, you may need to look for other website builders on the market.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the 9 most popular Wix alternatives and competitors you can use.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. WordPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wordpress-1.png\" alt=\"WordPress\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229506\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wordpress-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wordpress-1-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/wordpress-1-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WordPress is a free content management system (CMS) and website builder. It&#8217;s used by over 32% of websites around the globe, which makes it the most-used platform in the world. Many <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/\" title=\"46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively\">top brands use WordPress</a>  actively for their websites.</p>\n<p>By WordPress, we mean the self-hosted WordPress.org and not WordPress.com, a hosted solution. To avoid any confusion, we recommend you check out our in-depth article on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/\" title=\"WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org – Is One Really Better Than the Other?\">WordPress.com vs WordPress.org</a> for a full list of their differences.</p>\n<p>WordPress is a perfect alternative to Wix. Feel free to read our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wix-vs-wordpress/\" title=\"Wix vs. WordPress – Which One is the Best Choice? (Expert Review)\">Wix vs WordPress</a> for a complete side-by-side comparison. WordPress offers flexibility and customization that lacks in any other website builder. The themes and plugins in the WordPress repository help you design the website you need regardless of your skill level. Plus, you can find additional free and premium resources on the internet.</p>\n<p>Using WordPress will also give you a leg up on the competition if you need to build eCommerce sites. The <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce plugin</a> for WordPress is free to use and it allows you to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">create an online store</a> with ease. With WooCommerce, you can use any other WordPress plugins to extend the functionality of your online business.</p>\n<p>The WordPress community is all over the world. If you have any trouble with your site, you can ask about your issue on the forums and social channels. We bet you&#8217;ll get the solution in no time. You should also check out IsItWP&#8217;s <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/snippets/\" title=\"Snippets\">Snippets</a> section for more customization options.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/weebly/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Weebly\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Weebly</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/weebly/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Weebly\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly.png\" alt=\"Weebly\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229901\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/weebly-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Weebly is a popular website builder. It has tons of designs to create a website instantly. It&#8217;s a fully hosted solution which means you can get started using their site right away. Weebly has a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared\">drag and drop builder</a> to add text, images, and other content on your website.</p>\n<p>It also enables you to launch an online store and sell your products. Like your website, you won&#8217;t need external <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/free-web-hosting/\" title=\"Top 11 Best Free Web Hosting Companies (No B.S)\">web hosting</a> or bandwith for your eCommerce business. Everything is available on Weebly&#8217;s site, and you can start just by entering details about your store. They offer plenty of paid extensions to add more features to your website or online shop.</p>\n<p>Weebly has a strong support team to help resolve your issues. You can also use their community section to find a solution to any of your problems related to website making. Check out our complete <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/weebly-review/\" title=\"Weebly Review – Is It the Best Choice for You?\">Weebly review</a> for more details.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.squarespace.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Squarespace\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Squarespace</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squarespace.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Squarespace\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/squarespace.png\" alt=\"Squarespace\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229498\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/squarespace.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/squarespace-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/squarespace-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Squarespace is a self-hosted website and eCommerce store builder. It has multiple web templates for photographers, portfolio sites, restaurants, musicians, and more. These templates are highly professional and require little-to-no changes before you launch your website.</p>\n<p>It also comes with a powerful <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 BEST WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared\">eCommerce solution</a>. You can create a fully functional online store with Squarespace in just a few clicks of your mouse. Their product pages can be customized to add images, descriptions, and other information. You can use their premium payment solutions for secure transactions.</p>\n<p>Squarespace email campaigns help grow your website traffic. You can use their powerful tools to extend your reach and get more online visitors. Also, check out these <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-alternatives-to-squarespace/\" title=\"11 Squarespace Alternatives for Every Kind of Website\">Squarespace alternatives</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bigcommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"BigCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. BigCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bigcommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"BigCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bigcommerce.jpg\" alt=\"BigCommerce\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229503\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bigcommerce.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bigcommerce-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/bigcommerce-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>BigCommerce is an eCommerce platform used to create online business stores. It allows you to list your products on Facebook, Amazon, and other top social / business networks to get more business. It&#8217;s a premium solution, but you can start with a free trial to test their software.</p>\n<p>It can easily compete with Wix&#8217;s eCommerce builder. BigCommerce has solutions for small businesses, B2B, enterprises, and big online shops. It offers premium tools to create a powerful store. The apps integration adds more features to your site, and you can also accept online payments without owing any fees to them.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shopify\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Shopify</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shopify/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Shopify\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/shopify-1.png\" alt=\"Shopify\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229504\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/shopify-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/shopify-1-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/shopify-1-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Shopify is the most popular eCommerce platform on the market. It has a 14-day free trial to get to know the software and test everything before you setup your online store. You can use Shopify to sell online, on social media, on Amazon, or any other network. It&#8217;s a beginner-friendly solution with no coding skills required.</p>\n<p>If you plan to create an eCommerce shop with Wix, then you should also consider Shopify. With Shopify, you can manage unlimited products and inventory. It also allows you to track your orders and growth trends, so you&#8217;ll know your where you stand against your competitors.</p>\n<p>When it comes to website design, Shopify can be fully customized to change colors, fonts, backgrounds, and product page templates. You&#8217;ll be able to accept credit card payments, and it also integrates with other online payment solutions.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/webnode/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Webnode\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Webnode</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/webnode/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Webnode\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webnode-1.jpg\" alt=\"Webnode\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229500\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webnode-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webnode-1-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webnode-1-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Webnode is an excellent website builder and an alternative to Wix. It comes with free and premium plans to create a website. The free plan has basic features and allows you to set up a site on the Webnode domain name. To <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/domain-name-work/\" title=\"What is a Domain Name and How Does it Work? (Explained)\">register a custom domain name</a> and get other useful features, you&#8217;ll need their paid version.</p>\n<p>It has 50 web templates to design your site. These templates are free to use on Webnode. You can get started for free and upgrade to their premium plan when needed. The premium version has more to offer like a form builder, Google Analytics, email accounts, etc.</p>\n<p>Webnode has their own <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/free-web-hosting/\" title=\"Top 11 Best Free Web Hosting Companies (No B.S)\">web hosting</a> that&#8217;s included with any premium plan. You can upgrade your plan for more hosting space. The free version has less space, but it&#8217;s enough for a small website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/webstarts/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WebStarts\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. WebStarts</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/webstarts/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WebStarts\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webstarts-1.png\" alt=\"WebStarts\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229502\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webstarts-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webstarts-1-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/webstarts-1-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WebStarts is a freemium website builder. It has both free and premium plans. You can get started with their free version and scale to a premium plan later if you need more advanced features. WebStarts comes with a drag and drop page builder to instantly launch your website. It&#8217;s a cheap solution that&#8217;s perfect for startups.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a hosted platform and needs no outside resources to build a website. The highlighted features include membership addons, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">SEO tools</a>, contact forms, and more. You can talk with their live support team to get answers to any questions regarding your WebStarts website.</p>\n<p>WebStarts can also be used to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-start-a-blog-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Start a WordPress Blog (&#038; Make Extra Income)\">create a blog</a> or an online store. With all its features, you can use this platform to gain an online presence. It&#8217;s an alternative to Wix and other <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-website-builders-for-beginners-compared/\" title=\"10 Best Website Builders for Beginners Compared\">popular website builders</a> with more app integrations.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mozello/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mozello\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Mozello</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mozello/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mozello\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/mozello-1.png\" alt=\"Mozello\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229501\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/mozello-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/mozello-1-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/mozello-1-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Mozello is an excellent website building solution. It allows you to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-register-a-domain-name/\" title=\"Beginner’s Guide: How to Register a Domain Name (+ Tip on How to Get It for FREE)\">register a free domain name</a>. You can create a website, blog, or an online store with Mozello. Their premium plans have tons of amazing <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-content-marketing-tools-plugins-wordpress/\" title=\"15 Best Content Marketing Tools and Plugins for WordPress\">tools for marketing</a> and SEO. Plus, they include multilingual support so you can create a website in your native language.</p>\n<p>Like other website builders in this article, Mozello comes with a simple drag and drop module to quickly add elements and features onto your site. It has beautiful, professional designs to customize your website any way you want.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.jimdo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Jimdo\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Jimdo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jimdo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Jimdo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/jimdo-1.png\" alt=\"Jimdo\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229499\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/jimdo-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/jimdo-1-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/jimdo-1-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Jimdo is another website builder with powerful features to create a website. It&#8217;s based on artificial intelligence and understands users&#8217; requirements in a smart way. Jimdo offers a free domain name with their premium plans. Their excellent support team will help with all your website-related queries.</p>\n<p>This platform can also be used to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store – Step by Step (with Pictures)\">create an online store</a>. There&#8217;s no limit for adding products and no transaction fees. You can get the full profit of your sales when using Jimdo. It works great with popular payment solutions like PayPal and credit cards. You can also integrate SEPA Direct Card for online payments.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you discover the most popular Wix alternatives and competitors. You may also want to check out our guide on the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-alternatives-popular-wordpress-competitors/\" title=\"WordPress Alternatives – 18 Popular WordPress Competitors\">most popular WordPress alternatives</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-wix-alternatives/\">9 Best Wix Alternatives to Easily Build a Site (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-wix-alternatives/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"How to Pick the Best 